}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== The case of this model revision is '''black''', though it keeps the style used with earlier model EZXS88Ws. It bears the '''[[Cisco]]''' logo.
"A\N: GPCEB1050-000-PQ320", "P\N: GEB1050 Rev.PQ", "START: 2007/04/26", and model checkbox w/ options of '''GEB1050''' (checked) / '''GEH1050''' / '''GEB1055''' is silkscreened on one unit's board. .. as well as a date code of '''1023''' (June 2010). :Radial caps on the board are largely '''Lelon''' branded ( + one '''Chemi-Con''' and one w/ an unknown brand [just '''M''']). :The Switch IC has a small / moderate size heatsink adhered to it.
